author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Cheesecake Factory Reports Q1 Earnings Per Share Of $0.56
text:

* Q1 EARNINGS PER SHARE $0.56 * Q1 EARNINGS PER SHARE VIEW $0.68 â€” THOMSON REUTERS I/B/E/S
